"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係"},{"pid":"22f8ec9fd5d5ffac23f691b614ac2474ebf09d03","tid":2296841,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"其實做好預算, 裸辭本身都唔係問題"},{"pid":"6878e86d00492206b7498c8fbac59df2c1787c86","tid":2296841,"uid":312971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"我每日都倒數緊自己遞信嘅日子 真係留一日都嫌多"},{"pid":"eb37a2e7ab4364b1af7b3e2c1c1618b46b40d1e3","tid":2296841,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"唔邊搵工?"},{"pid":"910ad7a8049133a9698bfc8256d538c252d24824","tid":2296841,"uid":348098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb37a2e7ab4364b1af7b3e2c1c1618b46b40d1e3","tid":2296841,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:00:17.000Z","msg":"唔邊搵工?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"有搵<br />\n但係先搵咗半個月左右<br />\n預計就算順利都要兩個月先轉到工<br />\n不過呢排疫情又勁返<br />\n轉工無期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救命就嚟頂唔順個痴線老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eb4647c93d170aa36df638c6b2773ea4ca5f3e","tid":2296841,"uid":348098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbeecc352c6f311df395791a2b344711d2d35726","tid":2296841,"uid":288351,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"same 將會辭職<br />\n唔知大家生活情況點, 我就有地方住,只係負責家用同飲食開支,<br />\n我諗1個月大約使7千左右就OK, 1年就84000, 可能抖3個月咁上下過埋年先開始搵工, 預計用3個月時間搵工, 乜工都做下, 應該都唔使等一年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:38:27.000Z","msg":"我其實算好過好多人<br />\n大部分糧都自己袋<br />\n家用象徵式俾少少<br />\n所以都冇財政問題<br />\n最多搵到工前慳住用<br />\n不過儲緊錢上車<br />\n有同男朋友講過想裸辭<br />\n但係佢唔支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫我騎牛搵馬<br />\n好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa5741c7feca4796